Frequently Asked Questions

Q: Ni brown out ganina og kalit, mawala na ba ang akong oras?
A: No, naka save na kini sa among system ang imong oras ug nagdagan kini.

Q: Pwede ra ba na ni ugma gamiton ang akong voucher code?
A: Yes, anytime na nimo pwede ma login, pero kausa lang ni ang validity.

Q: Pwede ba ako mo utang og voucher code?
A: Yes, pero bayad intawn og sayo.

Q: Nganong wala ko ka dawat og promo nga naa may promo karon.
A: Please pahibaw-a mi kay basin naka limot ra ang nag bantay. Apan kung ikaw nangutang ra, dili ka makadawat og promo.

Weekend Promo

Please be informed that the promo is only effective every Saturday and Sunday.

Terms of Service

Effective as of April 2, 2021

Welcome to Pinoy Lifecraft Wifi Connect. The following Terms of Use apply once you are subjected to use the service. Please review the following terms carefully. By accessing or using our Service, you signify your agreement to these Terms of Use. If you do not agree to these Terms of Use, you may not use the service.

Privacy Policy

Please read the following information carefully to understand our practice regarding your data and how we will process data. We collect information from you only this things that matter, Wi-Fi MAC Address, and the voucher code you log in.

We need certain data in order to provide you with an access to the site. Once you log in with a voucher code, you will be asked to check on "agree to provide this information" in order to access our services, purchase voucher code, or view the login portal. If you do not agree to our use of your data in line with this policy, please do not use our service.

Information given includes the following:

Wi-Fi MAC Address > It stands for media access control address, it is a unique identifier assigned to a network interface controller for use as a network address in communications within a network segment. If you are using a phone or a tablet, you can find it under your device Settings > About Phone > Status.

Voucher Code you log in > Anyone can buy a voucher code, and once you log in, it is automatically collected to our server which includes the exact time you log in and when it will expire.

We may use your information as follows:
1. Track the voucher code you logged in from that device, if necessary.
2. Be able to know who logged in to the specific voucher code.
3. Block the device from using the service.

Refund Policy

Please review this refund policy first before making any inappropriate actions. If you have purchased a voucher code and changed your mind, please let us know right away so that we can refund you in a rightful way. We will still monitor the voucher code returned for record purposes. If dishonesty is proven, we will terminate your device without further notice.

Be aware that we do not issue a refund with the following cases:
1. The service is poor.
2. The service is no longer needed.
3. The internet speed is slow and you are dissatisfied far from the expectation.
4. Refund of the voucher code was not given right away after purchasing.
5. There was a sudden brown out and you requested to stop the service.
